e%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Latest%20Podcast%20Is%20A%20Lesson%20In%20Tech%20Outreach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20participated%20in%20two%20podcasts%2C%20engaging%20in%20nearly%20five%20hours%20of%20conversation%20on%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20topics.%20From%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20formative%20years%2C%20and%20governance%20philosophy%20to%20domestic%20politics%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20media%20narratives%2C%20and%20even%20the%202002%20post-Godhra%20Gujarat%20riots%E2%80%94Modi%20addressed%20it%20all.%20He%20also%20touched%20upon%20international%20affairs%2C%20offering%20his%20perspectives%20on%20President%20Trump%20and%20the%20U.S.%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20everyone%20may%20have%20watched%20these%20podcasts%20in%20their%20entirety%2C%20the%20wide-ranging%20discussions%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20something%20for%20everyone%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20supporters%20or%20critics.%20Notably%2C%20Modi%20embraced%20this%20increasingly%20popular%20medium%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20his%20third%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20signalling%20a%20shift%20in%20his%20outreach%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHosts%20Are%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20podcast%20hosts%20underscores%20a%20new%20approach.%20Modi's%20more%20than%20three-hour-long%20conversation%20with%20American%20computer%20scientist%20and%20podcaster%20Lex%20Fridman%2C%20released%20on%20Sunday%2C%20followed%20his%20previous%20two-hour%20discussion%20with%20Nikhil%20Kamath%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Zerodha%20and%20a%20well-known%20entrepreneur.%20Both%20Fridman%20and%20Kamath%20are%20accomplished%20figures%20in%20their%20respective%20fields%2C%20inspirational%20for%20young%20audiences.%20This%20dynamic%20adds%20a%20new%20dimension%20to%20Modi's%20freewheeling%20conversations%20with%20them%2C%20particularly%20for%20a%20demographic%20that%20looks%20up%20to%20such%20thought%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFridman%2C%20in%20announcing%20the%20release%20of%20his%20podcast%20with%20Modi%20to%20his%2046%20million%20social%20media%20followers%2C%20described%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20conversations%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20life.%20The%20rising%20popularity%20of%20podcasts%E2%80%94particularly%20among%20younger%20generations%20and%20those%20disenchanted%20with%20legacy%20media%E2%80%94offers%20a%20platform%20for%20in-depth%20discussions%20free%20from%20the%20constraints%20of%20traditional%20broadcast%20formats.%20Modi%20leveraged%20this%20format%20effectively%2C%20using%20extended%2C%20informal%20exchanges%20to%20discuss%20sensitive%20subjects%20such%20as%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20post-Godhra%20riots%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech-Driven%20Communication%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20embrace%20of%20new%20technologies%20and%20evolving%20communication%20strategies%20sets%20him%20apart.%20He%20always%20remains%20open%20to%20innovation%2C%20adapting%20to%20changing%20times%20and%20technological%20advancements.%20For%20instance%2C%20his%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20translate%20and%20deliver%20his%20podcasts%20and%20%E2%80%9CMann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%9D%20in%20multiple%20languages%20with%20his%20own%20voice%20is%20an%20example%20of%20an%20innovative%20and%20engaging%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20focus%20on%20technology%20also%20extends%20to%20governance%2C%20ensuring%20the%20efficient%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20transparent%20delivery%20of%20services%20through%20initiatives%20like%20the%20JAM%20trinity%E2%80%94Jan%20Dhan%2C%20Aadhaar%2C%20and%20Mobile.%20Modi%20explores%20both%20traditional%20and%20emerging%20mediums%20to%20strengthen%20his%20support%20base%20and%20reach%20new%20audiences%20who%20may%20not%20typically%20engage%20with%20daily%20political%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20ability%20to%20reinvent%20himself%20distinguishes%20him%20from%20his%20political%20peers%2C%20past%20and%20present.%20Those%20who%20have%20followed%20his%20career%20have%20witnessed%20his%20consistent%20experimentation%20with%20innovative%20engagement%20strategies.%20As%20Gujarat's%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20introduced%20the%20use%20of%20masks%20and%20holograms%E2%80%94creating%20simultaneous%203D%20appearances%20at%20multiple%20rallies%E2%80%94which%20sparked%20curiosity%20and%20debate%20beyond%20Gujarat's%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20pre-2014%20election%20initiative%20to%20connect%20with%20thousands%20of%20party%20workers%20through%20Audio%20Bridge%20is%20another%20example%20of%20his%20tech-savvy%20outreach.%20His%20first%20public%20engagement%20after%20being%20named%20the%20BJP's%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%202013%20was%20with%20aspirational%20students%20at%20Sri%20Ram%20College%20of%20Commerce.%20The%20%E2%80%9CChai%20pe%20Charcha%E2%80%9D%20initiative%20and%20his%20popularisation%20of%20selfies%20after%20voting%20were%20also%20initiatives%20that%20resonated%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpanding%20Digital%20Outreach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20the%20NaMo%20app%20also%20reflects%20Modi's%20commitment%20to%20two-way%20engagement%20beyond%20the%20BJP's%20traditional%20support%20base.%20The%20app%20attracted%20millions%20of%20users%20interested%20in%20his%20governance%20model%20and%20provided%20a%20platform%20for%20direct%20feedback.%20Modi%2C%20alongside%20the%20then%20BJP%20President%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20also%20pioneered%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmissed%20call%E2%80%9D%20membership%20drive%2C%20helping%20the%20BJP%20become%20the%20world's%20largest%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Modi%20has%20given%20interviews%20to%20numerous%20news%20channels%20and%20publications.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20took%20part%20in%20a%20candid%20interview%20with%20actor%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20Broadcast%20across%20all%20channels%2C%20the%20interview%20sought%20to%20showcase%20a%20softer%2C%20more%20relatable%20side%20of%20his%20persona%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20his%202019%20appearance%20on%20%E2%80%9CMan%20vs%20Wild%E2%80%9D%20with%20Bear%20Grylls%20at%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%20showcased%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20his%20personality%2C%20further%20broadening%20his%20appeal.%20As%20the%20first%20Indian%20political%20leader%20to%20recognise%20and%20harness%20the%20power%20of%20digital%20and%20social%20media%2C%20Modi%20has%20built%20an%20entirely%20new%20support%20base%20for%20himself%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20political%20parties%20have%20attempted%20to%20replicate%20his%20success%2C%20Modi%20has%20consistently%20stayed%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20evolving%20his%20communication%20strategy%20before%20others%20can%20catch%20up.%20His%20efforts%20to%20innovate%20and%20reinvent%20political%20engagement%20demonstrate%20his%20dynamic%20and%20ever-evolving%20approach%20to%20connecting%20with%20people%2C%20ensuring%20that%20he%20remains%20a%20step%20ahead%20in%20the%20digital%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742282760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fbis86hso_pm-modi-lex-fridman-ians_625x300_16_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpm-modis-latest-podcast-is-a-lesson-in-tech-outreach-7949848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi's%20efforts%20to%20innovate%20and%20reinvent%20political%20engagement%20demonstrate%20his%20dynamic%20and%20ever-evolving%20approach%20to%20connecting%20with%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A