a%20senior%20at%20St.%20Cloud%20State%20University%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20has%20remained%20under%20police%20surveillance%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic.%20He%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20for%20interrogation%20multiple%20times%2C%20his%20parents%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Konanki%20family%20sent%20a%20formal%20letter%20to%20authorities%20Monday%2C%20acknowledging%20there%20is%20no%20suspected%20foul%20play%20involved%20in%20Ms%20Konanki's%20presumed%20death%20after%20she%20vanished%20from%20a%20Punta%20Cana%20beach%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20March%206%2C%20New%20York%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20and%20mother%20also%20wrote%20they%20trust%20the%20authorities'%20probe%20into%20the%20case%20and%20noted%20Mr%20Riibe%2C%20the%20last%20person%20to%20see%20the%20young%20woman%20alive%2C%20has%20cooperated%20with%20investigators%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Konanki's%20parents%20said%20in%20the%20same%20letter%20that%20they%20understand%20that%20certain%20legal%20procedures%20must%20be%20followed%20for%20their%20request%2C%20but%20that%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20comply%20with%20any%20necessary%20formalities%20or%20documentation%2C%20sources%20were%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20ABC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Konanki%2C%20described%20by%20her%20father%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bambitious%26quot%3B%20student%20who%20planned%20to%20study%20medicine%2C%20arrived%20in%20Punta%20Cana%20on%20March%203.%20She%20travelled%20with%20five%20other%20female%20students%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Pittsburgh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Loudon%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Riibe%20said%20he%20first%20met%20Ms%20Konanki%20in%20the%20hotel%20when%20he%20and%20his%20friend%20introduced%20themselves%20to%20her%20group.%20The%20two%20friend%20groups%20went%20together%20to%20the%20bar%2C%20where%20they%20drank%20until%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20suggested%20we%2