%20its%20fight%20against%20extremism%20and%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20government%20in%20Dhaka%20said%20Gabbard's%20comments%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20based%20on%20any%20evidence%20or%20specific%20allegations%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20paint%20an%20entire%20nation%20with%20a%20broad%20and%20unjustified%20brush.%20Bangladesh%2C%20like%20many%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20has%20faced%20challenges%20of%20extremism%2C%20but%20it%20has%20continuously%20worked%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20international%20community%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20to%20address%20these%20issues%20through%20law%20enforcement%2C%20social%20reforms%2C%20and%20other%20counterterrorism%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20government%20said%20%26quot%3Bgroundlessly%20linking%20Bangladesh%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20'Islamist%20caliphate'%20undermines%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20countless%20Bangladeshis%20and%20their%20friends%20and%20partners%20around%20the%20world%20who%20are%20committed%20to%20peace%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20progress%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBangladesh%20strongly%20condemns%20any%20efforts%20to%20link%20the%20country%20to%20any%20form%20of%20'Islamist%20caliphate'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolitical%20leaders%20and%20public%20figures%20should%20base%20their%20statements%2C%20especially%20about%20the%20most%20sensitive%20issues%2C%20on%20actual%20knowledge%20and%20take%20care%20not%20to%20reinforce%20harmful%20stereotypes%2C%20to%20fan%20fears%20and%20potentially%20even%20stoke%20sectarian%20tensions.%20In%20support%20of%20our%20shared%20global%20efforts%20to%20combat%20extremism%20and%20terrorism%2C%20the%20Interim%20Government%20of%20Bangladesh%20remains%20committed%20to%20engaging%20in%20constructive%20dialogue%20based%20on%20facts%20and%20on%20respect%20for%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20security%20of%20all%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20interim%20government%20said.%3C%2