0difference%20to%20the%20chef%20from%20Honshu%2C%20Japan.%20Nobu%20Matsuhisa%20did%20not%20know%20what%20Robert%20De%20Niro%20was.%20He%20only%20knew%20the%20Godfather%20as%20a%20patron%20and%20served%20him%20food%20like%20he%20would%20any%20other%20guest%20at%20Matsuhisa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Nobus%20legendary%20Black%20Cod%20Miso%2C%20the%20dish%20that%20Robert%20De%20Niro%20fell%20in%20love%20with.%20Photo%3A%20Nobu%20Australia%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Nobus%20legendary%20Black%20Cod%20Miso%2C%20the%20dish%20that%20Robert%20De%20Niro%20fell%20in%20love%20with.%20Photo%3A%20Nobu%20Australia%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fj7djoaig_bacl-cod-miso-at-nobu_625x300_17_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENobu's%20legendary%20Black%20Cod%20Miso%2C%20the%20dish%20that%20Robert%20De%20Niro%20fell%20in%20love%20with.%20Photo%3A%20Nobu%20Australia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe%20Niro%20loved%20Nobu's%20Black%20Cod%20Miso.%20Soon%2C%20Matsuhisa%20found%20himself%20asking%20Robert%20-%20%26quot%3BBob%26quot%3B%20-%20to%20wait.%20De%20Niro%20suggested%20they%20work%20together%20on%20a%20new%20restaurant%20chain.%20Matsuhisa%20suggested%20they%20hold%20it%20off%20till%20he%20paid%20his%20cumulative%20debt%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Matsuhisa%20Beverly%20Hills%20found%20itself%20a%20place%20in%20Hollywood%20conversations.%20Four%20years%20since%20De%20Niro%20made%20Matsuhisa%20an%20offer%20he%20postponed%2C%20he%20picked%20up%20the%20phone%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20Nobu%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-one%20years%20since%20the%20first%20Nobu%20opened%20in%20New%20York%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20name%20to%20reckon%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarly%20To%20Rise%20And%20Early%20To%20Play%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENobu%20Melbourne%20is%20teeming%20with%20patrons%20on%20the%20evening%20we%20walk%20in%20and%20find%20a%20(high)%20table%